=== Pulling new patches ===

To update your tree from the master repositories, the quickest way is to use the {{{darcs-all}}} script:

{{{
  $ ./darcs-all pull -a
}}}

=== Submitting patches ===

To submit patches to the developers, please use {{{darcs send}}}.
